<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>LittleBlackBook</title>
    <link href="./static/styles.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body>
    <!-- Custom styles -->
    <style>
        /* Custom styles */
        body {
            background-color: #1a202c;
        }

        .btn {
            background-color: #4a5568;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #2d3748;
        }

        .btn:focus {
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(66, 153, 225, 0.5);
        }

        .footer-link:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8 text-white">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Welcome to LittleBlackBook</h1>
        <p class="text-lg mb-8">Your Personal Dating Companion</p>
        <div class="max-w-lg mx-auto">
            <p class="text-xl mb-4">Find Your Perfect Match, Every Time</p>
            <p class="text-lg mb-8">Tired of endless swiping? LittleBlackBook revolutionizes the dating game by
                intelligently collecting and analyzing your dating data to help you find your ideal partner
                effortlessly.
                Say goodbye to guesswork and hello to meaningful connections.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="max-w-lg mx-auto">
            <p class="text-xl mb-4">How It Works</p>
            <ol class="list-decimal pl-5 mb-8">
                <li class="text-lg">Data Collection: LittleBlackBook seamlessly gathers information about your dating
                    preferences, experiences, and interactions.</li>
                <li class="text-lg">Data Aggregation: Our advanced algorithms aggregate and organize your dating data,
                    creating a comprehensive profile of your romantic journey.</li>
                <li class="text-lg">Inferences and Insights: Using cutting-edge technology, LittleBlackBook generates
                    insights and recommendations tailored to your unique preferences, increasing your chances of finding
                    true compatibility.</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
        <div class="max-w-lg mx-auto">
            <p class="text-xl mb-4">Features</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mb-8">
                <li class="text-lg">Smart Matching: Discover potential matches based on your past experiences and
                    preferences.</li>
                <li class="text-lg">Personalized Recommendations: Receive tailored suggestions for activities, venues,
                    and conversation starters based on your interests.</li>
                <li class="text-lg">Insightful Analytics: Gain valuable insights into your dating patterns and behaviors
                    to enhance your future experiences.</li>
                <li class="text-lg">Privacy Protection: Rest assured, your data is securely encrypted and will never be
                    shared without your consent.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
            <a href="#" class="btn py-3 px-6 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold inline-block">Sign Up Now</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-gray-900 text-white py-8">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
            <div class="flex justify-center mb-4">
                <a href="#" class="mr-4 footer-link">Facebook</a>
                <a href="#" class="mr-4 footer-link">Instagram</a>
                <a href="#" class="footer-link">Twitter</a>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
                <p class="mb-2">&copy; 2024 LittleBlackBook. All rights reserved.</p>
                <div>
                    <a href="#" class="mr-4 footer-link">Privacy Policy</a>
